  <!-- EN: frontier weapons -->
  <VWEFT_FrontierWeapons.label>边境武器</VWEFT_FrontierWeapons.label>
  <!-- EN: Craft frontier guns like revolvers, rifles, and shotguns. -->
  <VWEFT_FrontierWeapons.description>解锁制作左轮手枪、步枪、霰弹枪等边境枪械。</VWEFT_FrontierWeapons.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->echoes of the frontier</li>
    <li>subject_story->revived the rugged spirit of the frontier, crafting firearms that embody the essence of survival and exploration</li>
    <li>subject_story->perfected the art of gunsmithing to produce revolvers, rifles, and shotguns, tools as much for defense as for forging ahead into the unknown</li>
    <li>subject_story->imbued each weapon with the reliability and durability needed to face the untamed wilds and protect burgeoning communities</li>
